OL,4,G1040FThe Alfred Hitchcock Hour
OL,5,     GI'll Be Judge - I'll Be Jury:
OL,6,     GRelatives of a murdered newlywed
OL,7,     Gdecide to bring the killer to
OL,8,     Gjustice themselves.
OL,9,G1140FThe Alfred Hitchcock Hour
OL,10,     GThe Lonely Hours: While renting a
OL,11,     Groom at a farmhouse, a deranged
OL,12,     Gwoman becomes fascinated by a
OL,13,     Gseven-month-old boy who she
OL,14,     Gbelieves is her son.
OL,15,G1240FChicago
OL,16,     GIn 1920s Chicago, slick lawyer
OL,17,     GRichard Gere does his best to get
OL,18,     Gshowbiz jailbirds Catherine Zeta-
OL,19,     GJones and Renee Zellweger off the
OL,20,     Ghook. Dazzling winner of six
OL,21,     GOscars.
